title: Bonus Episode – The Alibi
description:
December 9, 2019 / Pedro Reynoso was convicted of a double homicide in Philadelphia in 1991, but new evidence points to a strong alibi and the true perpetrator of the crime. 
 
Episode scoring music by Animal Weapon.
